    "body": "Hiya :) There was an issue trying to recreate the project with the sandbox, but was receiving the error that the instantsearch.css package was [missing a semi colon](https://github.com/codesandbox/codesandbox-client/issues/6235). At the moment we are using the version 3.0.0.beta-5 and were wondering whether there were plans to release a stable version 3, otherwise we are looking into upgrading our angular app to use algolia instant search v4.",
